  <entry>
    <title>[问题处理]SVN踩得几个坑</title>
    <link href="http://ted423.github.io/Issue/svn/"/>
    <id>http://ted423.github.io/Issue/svn/</id>
    <published>2021-07-29T02:03:43.287Z</published>
    <updated>2021-10-09T02:42:27.417Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="The-server-sent-a-truncated-HTTP-response-body"><a href="#The-server-sent-a-truncated-HTTP-response-body" class="headerlink" title="The server sent a truncated HTTP response body"></a>The server sent a truncated HTTP response body</h1><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/ad53304dbdbf">https://www.jianshu.com/p/ad53304dbdbf</a><br>印象里这篇文章似乎没啥用，后面是要改apache的设置。</p><h1 id="备份"><a href="#备份" class="headerlink" title="备份"></a>备份</h1><p>大部分文章都强调不能cp和rsync。但结果来说，rsync可能会成为最终结果</p><ol><li>SVN并没有提供直接备份所有repo的办法，所有文章的repo都是基于单个repo的，所以要备份只能遍历。</li><li>svnadmin dump 出来的文件比服务器上的repo还要大。</li><li>svnadmin dump 的某个repo只有1kb，空repo也是1kb。手动备份能正常备份，<strong>所以记得一定要开log</strong></li><li>svnadmin hotcopy卡住，网上看跟文件系统有关，大概我用的NTFS</li></ol><h1 id="验证相关"><a href="#验证相关" class="headerlink" title="验证相关"></a>验证相关</h1><p>1.8 新增了一个设置，默认关了权限继承</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">AuthzSVNAuthoritative On|Off</span><br><span class="line">Set to Off to allow access control to be passed along to lower modules. The default value of this directive is On.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多见这里<br><a href="https://svnbook.red-bean.com/en/1.8/svn.serverconfig.httpd.html">https://svnbook.red-bean.com/en/1.8/svn.serverconfig.httpd.html</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
